1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Welcome. You cannot imagine how glad I am that you are already here.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,599
I am Cero, a member of Organization ADN.

3
00:00:07,599 --> 00:00:12,000
For years we have been investigating what makes some human groups

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:14,800
able to go farther than the rest.

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:19,199
Why are there teams that, together, can achieve milestones that seem impossible.

6
00:00:19,199 --> 00:00:21,399
After a long time analyzing data,

7
00:00:21,399 --> 00:00:25,000
we have identified a very small number of groups with

8
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:30,800
unique potential. You are one of them. Thousands of years ago, humanity already showed what it

9
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:35,399
can do when many people share a common goal.

10
00:00:35,399 --> 00:00:41,119
Colossal works, legacies that still amaze us today. Among all of them, one rises

11
00:00:41,119 --> 00:00:45,500
as a symbol of balance, effort, and precision: the pyramid.

12
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:51,200
Today we will evaluate your skills as a team, and you will have to overcome a series of challenges

13
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:59,200
to build your own pyramid, a construction made of coordination, ingenuity, and trust.

14
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:04,900
To overcome these tests, you will need the ten terminals distributed around the room,

15
00:01:04,900 --> 00:01:05,239
and some pyramid tokens that we will hand out to each group.

16
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:10,400
And some pyramid tokens that we will hand out to each group. These tokens will be

17
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:15,560
non-transferable. To use them, you must place them on the square mark on the

18
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:22,280
top of the terminals. A warning: we do not allow interference here. Phones and external

19
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:30,359
accessories are forbidden. Your only tools will be what you have in front of you and your ability to collaborate.

20
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:33,359
For now, this is all I can tell you.

21
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:35,840
Prove that you are a capable team.
